      <title>美国共和党考虑特朗普两步立法议程</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senate-republicans-eye-two-step-trump-legislative-agenda-2024-12-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国会共和党正在讨论一项分两步走的计划，以便在明年控制两院后推进当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的议程，可能首先从边境安全、能源和国防开始，然后再转向减税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senate-republicans-eye-two-step-trump-legislative-agenda-2024-12-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 23:16:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
